# TMDB 电影宇宙 — Project Overview

A 2.5D immersive movie-history archive: ~60K TMDB films rendered as a particle galaxy.
- **X/Y**: UMAP coordinates from text embeddings + genre weights + language one-hot
- **Z**: release_date as decimal year (not fed to UMAP)
- **Visual**: vote_count → particle size (log), vote_average → bloom/emissive, genres[0] → color

## Architecture

- **Python pipeline** (`scripts/`): CSV cleaning → NLP embedding → UMAP → export `galaxy_data.json`
- **Frontend** (`frontend/`): Vite + TypeScript + React (HUD/DOM) + raw Three.js (3D canvas) + Zustand (bridge)
- **Deployment**: static hosting (Vercel); no backend server in current phase

