## Critical Constraints

- UMAP `random_state=42` — always fixed
- Genre weight ratio default `1/φ ≈ 0.618` — configurable but version-bumped on change
- Multilingual sentence-transformers only (never English-only models)
- Z axis keeps raw decimal-year scale (~1874–2026); no normalization
